How To make This Work
---------------------

1. Install docutils (http://docutils.sourceforge.net)
2. Install Mako (http://makotemplates.org)
3. Install doit (http://python-doit.sourceforge.net)

To build or update the site::

    doit

To see the contents::

    doit -a serve

And point your browser to http://localhost:8000

You can even have doit rebuild the site automatically by running::

    doit auto

Nikola automatically generates a Google sitemap for your site. For information
about how to make sitemaps useful for your site, please read FIXME: missing URL

